<reg_short_dscr>:
FIFO delay measurement
------------------------------
<reg_public_text>:
FIFO delay measurement register
------------------------------
<field_public_text>:
Link-up dynamic delay to be added to the PTP TX I/O link delay configuration. 
Value is the fraction of 65536 of the maximum delay at a given speed and lane index.

1.0 Gbps: 128 ns
2.5 Gbps: 51.2 ns
5.0 Gbps : 15.5 ns (lane 0-12), 49.6 ns (lane 13-24)
10.0 Gbps: 24.8ns

NOTE: Lane 25+ have different delays than these.
------------------------------
<field_public_text>:
Link-up dynamic delay to be added to the PTP RX I/O link delay configuration. 
Value is the fraction of 65536 of the maximum delay at a given speed and lane index.

1.0 Gbps: 64 ns
2.5 Gbps: 25.6 ns
5.0 Gbps : 12.4 ns (lane 0-12), 37.2 ns (lane 13-24)
10.0 Gbps: 18.6 ns

Example: Value on lane 22 running at 5 Gbps is 25000.
Add 25000/65536*37.2 ns = 14.2 ns to PTP RX I/O delay for port 53 (serdes mapping)

NOTE: Lane 25+ have different delays than these.
------------------------------
